{{Quote|A Hutt without a sail barge is like a smoke moth without wings.|translated=1|[[Huttese/Legends|Huttese]] saying|<ref name="TNEGtVaV" />}}
The '''''Luxury''-class sail barge''' was a large [[Repulsorlift/Legends|repulsorlift]] [[Sail barge/Legends|sail barge]] produced by [[Ubrikkian Industries/Legends|Ubrikkian Industries]] during the time of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]].

==Characteristics==
[[File:Sailbarge_schem.jpg|thumb|left|180px|Sail barge [[:Category:Technical drawing images|schematics]]]]

The ''Luxury''-class sail barge had a top speed of one hundred kilometers per hour over a variety of relatively flat terrain, including water or sand, or a speed of thirty kilometers per hour relying solely on its large sails for propulsion.<ref name="SWTJ" /> The primary propulsion system was generally a three-chambered [[Repulsorlift/Legends|repulsorlift]] engine. A pair of decorate steering vanes at the stern of the vessel provided the vessel with its maneuvering capabilities. The entire vessel was powered by a series of batteries and power cells at the forward part of the vessel.<ref name="SWTJ" /><ref name="Incredible Cross Sections">''[[Star Wars: Incredible Cross-Sections]]''</ref>

It required a crew of twenty-six to fly, and could handle up to five hundred passengers and two thousand metric tons of cargo. In order to keep the vessel cool, an air conditioning unit was installed.<ref name="SWTJ" />

==History==
[[File:Strafing_Run_EotE_by_Mark_Molnar.jpg|thumb|right|250px|A ''Luxury''-class sail barge attacked by [[Storm IV Twin-Pod cloud car/Legends|cloud cars]]]]
Sail barges were commonly popular amongst [[Hutt/Legends|Hutt]] [[Crime lord/Legends|crime lords]], since the vessels allowed them to travel in style along with their retinue. [[Jabba Desilijic Tiure/Legends|Jabba Desilijic Tiure]] owned a modified, armed version of the Ubrikkian barge, named [[Khetanna/Legends|''Khetanna'']]. This vessel was destroyed by its own deck-mounted [[Blaster cannon/Legends|blaster cannon]], fired by [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]], during the rescue of [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] at the [[Battle of the Great Pit of Carkoon]] on [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]].

